====Usage notes====
* This character, <big>兹</big> which contains {{l|zh|䒑}} (3 strokes) is the orthodox form used in mainland China. <!-- See also Character 1653 - https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/通用規范漢字表 -->
* The character <span style="font-size:large;" lang=zh-hant>[[茲#Chinese|茲]]</span> (<code>U+8332</code>) which contains span style="font-size: large;" lang=zh-hant>[[艹#Chinese|艹]]</span> (grass radical, 4 strokes in {{w|traditional Chinese}}) is the orthodox form used in modern Taiwan. <!-- Refer https://www.moedict.tw/茲 -->

